I tried to stop him.

781
00:39:13,067 --> 00:39:14,967
Then your efforts were lacking.

782
00:39:15,003 --> 00:39:17,402
Not only did your
friend destroy everything

783
00:39:17,438 --> 00:39:20,338
we've been working
towards, he also got away.

784
00:39:22,009 --> 00:39:24,376
We put too much trust in you.

785
00:39:24,411 --> 00:39:28,278
Your ties to S.H.I.E.L.D. are
stronger than you admit.

786
00:39:28,315 --> 00:39:30,847
Leaves me with questions.

787
00:39:34,054 --> 00:39:36,952
No.

788
00:39:36,989 --> 00:39:39,722
You were right to trust me.

789
00:39:39,757 --> 00:39:42,692
I'm finished with S.H.I.E.L.D.

790
00:39:42,728 --> 00:39:45,561
And actually, I have answers.

791
00:39:45,597 --> 00:39:48,565
The DNA you need... I have it.

792
00:39:48,599 --> 00:39:50,134
Inhuman DNA is not enough.

793
00:39:50,168 --> 00:39:52,135
We needed to drain actual Kree blood.

794
00:39:52,170 --> 00:39:54,702
Which is what I have pumping
through my veins.

795
00:39:54,739 --> 00:39:58,173
Coulson used it to bring
me back after Quinn shot me.

796
00:39:58,208 --> 00:39:59,775
Ward should remember.

797
00:40:01,211 --> 00:40:02,545
He does.

798
00:40:02,579 --> 00:40:08,251
So, if you want this
experiment to work...

799
00:40:08,286 --> 00:40:10,362
drain me.

